title: Pluralsight - Windows Azure Marketplace
description: The Windows Azure Marketplace provides a large global collection of cloud-scale data sets which can easily be consumed by Excel, PowerPivot, Tableau, LINQPad, or any OData capable application. This course introduces the wide variety of useful data sets and demonstrates easy access by non-technical users or .NET application developers. In addition, this course shows how to list your application in the Marketplace and how to publish your own data set, for free and/or for monthly subscription income, to a global audience with just a few steps
